snippet.title: Tetris Attack (Super NES) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more videos!

Visit my blog:
vgruairi.blogspot.com

Gameplay video of 'Tetris Attack' for the Super NES, a fantastic puzzle game that later became known as Puzzle League. 'Tetris Attack' was released near the end of the Super NES' lifespan, so didn't get the publicity it deserved. It's aged very well, and has a mean multiplayer mode.
